item.title: CVE-2023-28387|2024-08-02T12:38:25.109Z -- newspicks%2C%20inc. -- %22newspicks%22%20app%20for%20android
item.description: "NewsPicks" App for Android versions 10.4.5 and earlier and "NewsPicks" App for iOS versions 10.4.2 and earlier use hard-coded credentials, which may allow a local attacker to analyze data in the app and to obtain API key for an external service.
